cab.content: SECRETOPERATIONS.Prom:Advanced G .H .QFranceTo:-C .1 .G.S Far Office.30.10.17.'handed in at 10-37 p.m.received11-30 p.m.0 A'B/1. .'Po 11 owing from H.Q-., R.P.C. in addition toPress Communique.. Message begins. Many machines on night of29th-30th started for Saarbrucken, but only a few couldfind the objective owing to the weather. The remainingmachines returned with their bombs. Message ends.
